CLONE REPOSITORY
git clone link-of-repository

MASUK FOLDER-REPO
cd nama-repo

INISIALISASI GIT
git init

CONNECT REPO TO GITHUB
git remote add origin https://github.com/username/nama-repo.git

STAGING SAVE PERUBAHAN
git add .

COMMIT CHANGE
git commit -m "Commit Message"

PUSH 2 GITHUB
git push -u origin master

PULL REPO
git pull origin main

PUSH UPDATE 2 GITHUB
git add .
git commit -m "New Update ato apa kek"
git push

IDENTITAS COMMIT UNTUK SEMUA REPO
git config --global user.name "Username"
git config --global user.email "Email"

IDENTITAS COMMIT UNTUK INDIVIDUAL REPO
git config user.name "Username"
git config user.email "Email"

LIHAT IDENTITAS COMMITER
git config --list

CEK REMOTE REPO 
git remote -v

REMOTE REPO
git remote set-url origin https://github.com/Username/Reponame.git

- TUTORIAL MENGGANTI AKUN VS-CODE GITHUB!
1. Klik logo window dan cari Credential Manager
2. Masuk Windows Credentials
3. Cari git:https://github.com lalu klik
4. Remove.
5. Di terminal masukkan git push origin main
6. Login ulang.
Jangan lupa buat ganti Commiter Account dengan Identitas commit di terminal.

